					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Services Section -->
	<section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
		<div class="container-max">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">
					Check out our service offerings
				</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<!-- Comprehensive Bookkeeping -->
				<div class="card p-8">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-6726b3ff858f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2340&q=80" alt="Bookkeeping Services" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-6" />
					<h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">
						Comprehensive Bookkeeping
					</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						At <strong>IBATS CORP.</strong>, we provide <strong>comprehensive bookkeeping services</strong> to keep your <strong>financial records accurate, organized, and up-to-date</strong>. Our expert team manages everything from <strong>daily transaction recording</strong> to <strong>accounts payable and receivable</strong>, ensuring seamless financial operations.
					</p>
					<a href="/services/bookkeeping" class="btn-primary">Learn More</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Expert Accounting Services -->
				<div class="card p-8">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2415&q=80" alt="Accounting Services" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-6" />
					<h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">
						Expert Accounting Services
					</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						At <strong>IBATS Corp</strong>, we provide <strong>expert accounting services</strong> tailored to strengthen your business's financial foundation. Our comprehensive solutions include <strong>financial statement preparation, budget analysis, and forecasting</strong>, ensuring you have the insights needed for strategic decision-making.
					</p>
					<a href="/services/accounting" class="btn-primary">Learn More</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Tax Planning and Preparation -->
				<div class="card p-8">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224154-26032fbc4d72?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2340&q=80" alt="Tax Services" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-6" />
					<h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">
						Tax Planning and Preparation
					</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						At <strong>IBATS CORP.</strong>, we provide <strong>professional tax planning and preparation services</strong> for <strong>businesses and individuals</strong>. Our experienced tax specialists stay updated on the latest <strong>tax laws and regulations</strong>, ensuring you claim every <strong>deduction, credit, and tax-saving opportunity</strong> available.
					</p>
					<a href="/services/corporate-income-tax" class="btn-primary">Learn More</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="text-center mt-12">
				<a href="/services" class="btn-secondary">
					Learn more about all our services
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Testimonials Section -->
	<section class="section-padding bg-white">
		<div class="container-max">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">
					See what people are saying
				</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<!-- Testimonial 1 -->
				<div class="card p-8">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
							<span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">L</span>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-900">Salah Mansieh</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">CFO, LB Supply</p>
						</div>
					</div>
