						"As a growing e-commerce business in the GTA, we needed a remote bookkeeping service that could handle our complex structure from anywhere. For almost three years, their services have been consistently excellent. They are true experts in the field, always responsive, and genuinely helpful."
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Testimonial 2 -->
				<div class="card p-8">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
							<span class="text-purple-600 font-bold">A</span>
						</div>
						<div>
