						</div>
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-600 italic leading-relaxed">
						"IBATS Corp has been invaluable in the bookkeeping and accounting of our agency. Since switching our accounts to the team at IBATS we have received such great service and their insights into our books have helped us save money and improve the systems we use to manage our revenue and resources. We're going to be long-term customers going forward!"
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Testimonial 3 -->
				<div class="card p-8">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
							<span class="text-green-600 font-bold">F</span>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-900">Francis Campbell</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Owner, Supreme Suds</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-600 italic leading-relaxed">
						"I own a small local business here in Niagara, and while I've always been great at what I do, I definitely struggled with the backend stuff—especially when I was first starting out and everything got chaotic. After trying four different accountants from a previous company and now with my current business, I can honestly say that IBATS Corp and the team are exactly what I needed. They're incredibly knowledgeable and clearly take great pride in their work. Definitely a 5+ star accounting team! Thanks so much, IBATS Corp"
